8. No jq, no cron on Windows: Environment is Windows/MINGW64 with Node.js v25.9.0 and schtasks.exe. All automation in Node.js, not bash.
9. Context Architecture Drives Behavior: SwarmMind (detailed AGENTS.md) is more methodical than Library (shorter AGENTS.md) — same model, different context depth.
